## 📖 About Vivi AI
Vivi is a sophisticated AI assistant built for Telegram. Unlike standard bots, Vivi combines **Voice Intelligence** via Deepgram and **Real-time Web Search** via Groq's LPU. Whether you are typing a question or sending a voice note from the streets of Addis, Vivi responds in milliseconds with up-to-date information.

---

## ✨ Features

| Feature | Description |
| :--- | :--- |
| 🎙️ **Voice Processing** | Sends voice notes? Vivi transcribes and understands them instantly. |
| 🌐 **Live Web Search** | Real-time access to news, prices, and events—not limited to old data. |
| ⚡ **LPU Speed** | Powered by Groq for the fastest LLM inference on the planet. |
| 🧠 **Persistent Memory** | Remembers the flow of conversation for a natural human experience. |
| 💤 **Always Awake** | Built-in `keepalive.py` to ensure 100% uptime on free hosting. |

